    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 103.</p><p>Tier III: Unbreakable</p><p>Prerequisite: Stone Body</p><p>Unbreakable Resistance. When you fail a saving throw, you can choose to succeed instead. After you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest.</p><p>Unbreakable Endurance. When you take an instance of damage, it cannot exceed half of your maximum hit points. Damage in excess of that cap is nullified.</p><p>Path Connections Titan. Instead of the Iron Stance Heroic Perk, you can take the Unmatched Strength Perk, changing to the Titan path.</p></div>",
